{"tid":367134,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"謝拉特：阿仙奴好易對付","createTime":"2017-08-20T13:49:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T12:41:06.000Z","uid":16659,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"26cb77d5d8b1c9e168b967ec7d67b90053eaa979","tid":367134,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T13:49:07.000Z","msg":"阿仙奴開季第2場以0：1不敵史篤城，下輪比賽將鬥利物浦。紅軍傳奇球星謝拉特說，其實阿仙奴很易應付。<br />\n<br />\n經過首場驚險4：3勝李斯特城之後，阿仙奴今場以0：1不敵史篤城，謝斯洛迪古斯的入球令到阿仙奴全失3分，兵工廠在開季第2輪已經嘗到輸波滋味。<br />\n<br />\n今場比賽，兵工廠控球率高達77.3%，是自03/04球季之後最高的一次，不過始終未能將控球轉化為攻門及入球。<br />\n<br />\n謝拉特分析了阿仙奴的毛病：「要在英超成為強隊，控球率非常重要，阿仙奴控球能力的確很強。不過他們強於控球，卻不願意去主動碰撞對抗。阿仙奴的問題是太多技術型天才在正選陣容，沒有一些硬漢、勇於對抗的人在陣中。只是空有控球率，未來表現也會這樣。」<br />\n<br />\n阿仙奴下場比賽是作客利物浦，8月27日作賽。(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=A2FilI2z%2B5TCIr3KZpWVfNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=ee249286\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"8a48934edd8b11736cea59ef47305d7540012595","tid":367134,"uid":1984,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T13:50:42.000Z","msg":"無左你助攻緊係易"},{"pid":"1c582b7545a756dde9ddc7ec2af34319c0b02651","tid":367134,"uid":42152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T13:50:50.000Z","msg":"雲加換人柒啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb7cd017f8eb624773a298010d47dee1520c3079","tid":367134,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T13:50:50.000Z","msg":"君子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"720ef6f1e2184f3405c527f154ed22af77f3441c","tid":367134,"uid":581,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T13:51:14.000Z","msg":"下場就炒你死利狗"},{"pid":"790f1cb9b62c1dd5191f331d0537f271076d2882","tid":367134,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T13:51:29.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"c0f37eabda01f3937d8d2395ed52a27fe033dd35","tid":367134,"uid"